data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! Don't miss out on your opportunity to own this amazing 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in the highly sought out community of Champions Reserve in Davenport, FL! Located in a community with low HOA, the home sits on a quiet cul-de-sac. Built in 2020-This home has it all!  The Seagate floor plan is thoughtfully designed with 2 bedrooms on one wing, 1 bedroom on the other side and the primary bedroom suite completely split from the others. Recently painted interior in 2022, exterior painted October 2023, tiles replaced in Sept 2021, carpets in all rooms replaced in 2021.  This home has tons of upgrades with granite countertops throughout the home.  The kitchen boasts an upgraded extra large kitchen island for entertaining as well as gorgeous backsplash, and stainless steel appliances.  The upgraded blinds and ceilings fans in all rooms will stay.  Brand New Fence installed in 2020! Step out to your covered lanai area and privately fenced in backyard that in perfect for spending evenings and weekends in.  The home already has drain gutters in place, and the extended paved driveway adds to the home's beautiful curb appeal.    Champions Reserve is a gorgeous community located right next to Champions Gate! Amenities include resort-style pool, clubhouse, tot lot, pocket parks, and easy commute onto I-4 and 429.  Located in the heart of Disney and close to all the theme parks!  Schedule your showing today!
